{% extends 'TOEICTrainerBundle::base.html.twig' %}
{% block title %}{{ parent() }}Home{% endblock %}
{% block completebody %}
    <div class="jumbotron">
        <h1>Welcome to TOEIC Trainer !</h1>
        <p>TOEIC Trainer is a website to help you improve your english by doing TOEIC like exercises. Like the real TOEIC, our test his constituted of two distinct part : a Listening part and a Reading part.</p>
    </div>
    {% block body %}
    <div class="row">

        <div class="col-sm-6">
            <div class="panel panel-info">
              <div class="panel-heading">
                <h4 class="panel-title">Listening part</h4>
              </div>
              <div class="panel-body">
                <p>The listening part of the test is composed of four different exercises. </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        In the first exercise we have photography and 
                        description, the goal of this exercise is to find the 
                        description that best correspond to the photography. 
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        In the second exercise we hear question and multiple 
                        answer and we have to find the best answer for 
                        the question. 
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        For the third exercise we hear conversations and read 
                        questions, the goal is to select the correct written 
                        answer to the question. 
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Finally, in the last exercise we hear talks and read 
                        question and the goal is to select the answer that 
                        correspond to the question.
                    </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
        </div>


        <div class="col-sm-6">
            <div class="panel panel-info">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h4 class="panel-title">Reading part</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="panel-body">
                    <p>The reading part is composed of three different exercises. </p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            The first exercise consists in filling the 
                            blanks in incomplete sentences.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            In the second exercise, we have to fill the 
                            blanks in a whole text.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            And finally in the last exercise, we have multiple 
                            documents and questions, of which you have to answer 
                            correctly using the information in the documents.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    {% endblock %}
{% endblock %}
